title: Lovely Historic with Modern Flair-614 Portland Ave St Paul
posting_body: ['BASE RENT IS ONLY $1350', 'The Clubhouse, built in 1913, is a stunning combination of past and present with 40 beautifully designed apartments.', 'This grand representative of the historic Summit Hill neighborhood of St. Paul originally housed gymnasium, pool, and bowling alley for the Episcopal Church of St Paul, before transitioning into luxury apartment homes.', 'Apartments retain many original features like high ceilings, pristine woodwork, and oversized windows, while also offering modern touches like granite counters, spacious layouts, updated appliances and air conditioning.', 'The location just off Summit and Grand Avenues can’t be beat!', 'You will have a plethora of shopping and restaurant options within steps of your home, while also having easy access to interstates 94 and 35 and the greater metro area.', 'Come make this landmark your home.', 'We currently have two two bedroom styles (ranging in price from $1400-$1595)available over the next two months.', ' One has its own private entrance!', '- Laundry on site', '- Free parking', '- Super maintenance', '- High ceilings', '- Dishwashers', 'Contact Eric -', 'show contact info', 'Professionally managed by the Hornig Companies']
